            "failure_message": "Requires sustained attachment + lonely yearning with a loss spike (grief or sadness), grounded in negative valence and high engagement. Future expectancy and self-evaluation dip to give the crash its 'hopeless/personal' edge. Blocks numbness/dissociation (must stay raw) and blocks rage-dominance (not a bitter/hostile variant). Triggers only on a grief/sadness spike OR a hard valence drop while love_attachment remains high."
